# US ratings:
#   A+ 10   A 9   A- 8
#   B+ 7    B 6   B- 5
#   C+ 4    C 3   C- 2
#   D+ 1.5  D 1   D- 1
#   E 0.5   F 0
# indiewire does C => 4
# Le film français+Screen Daily+Media Cine+cahier 0-4: 0: 1, 1: 2.5, 2: 5, 3: 7.5, 4: 9
# ch,dk,ru,FNE 1-5: x2
# British 0-5: x2
# critic.de +++ 9, ++ 7.5, + 6, +- 5, - 4, -- 2.5, --- 1
